steps.name: I select make as "Mitsubishi" and model as "Outlander" in the Select Your Car fields
I check the checkbox "I am NOT eligible to claim the dealership discount"

arguments.val: I am NOT eligible to claim the dealership discount

steps.name: I select the "Universal Socket" option under Select your connection type
I check the prices for the "7kw" unit displayed under Select your power rating match Full Price – "£879.00"
I check the prices for the "7kw" unit displayed under Select your power rating match With OLEV Grant - "£529.00"
I check that "6" compatible extras are shown
I select a random compatible extra
I ensure that the total price at the bottom right of the screen correctly matches the "7kw" unit price plus the compatible extra price
